  "content": "we need an idea more of an start up idea"
}

[agent/message]
From principal:{
  "content": "do some market reserch ans tellme"
}

[agent/message]
From executive_organization_1:{
  "content": "Your objective is to conduct market research on current high-potential AI startup opportunities. Please identify 3-5 promising niches, analyze the market gaps, and propose specific AI tool concepts. Focus on areas where AI can solve clear, actionable pain points for either consumers or businesses. Report your findings back to me."
}

[agent/review_presentation_response]
From auditor_service:{
  "summary": "PASS: The submission meets all acceptance criteria: 3 niches were identified, each with documented market gaps, and each is supported by 2 credible, recent industry sources. The analysis aligns with current industry focus areas and provides actionable intelligence. No regressions or gaps identified.",
  "taskId": "task_1"
}

[agent/review_presentation_response]
From auditor_service:{
  "summary": "PASS: The submission successfully meets the acceptance criteria for the task. It provides three distinct, actionable AI tool concepts (OrchestraAgent, ComplianceLens AI, EdgeSmart Robotics Manager) corresponding to the specified niches (Enterprise, Vertical/BFSI, Physical/Manufacturing). Each concept includes a clearly defined target audience, a specific pain point being addressed, and a viable competitive differentiation. The concepts are technically grounded and address current market needs regarding enterprise integration, regulatory compliance (XAI), and edge computing/data privacy in industrial settings.",
  "taskId": "task_2"
}
